name: o11.1 — Mundanity — rev. 13.1 "Overdue Entry"
description:
Not everything has meaning, there is no point in looking for it. 

Consciously, I accepted that searching for the meaning (especially of life) is counterproductive most of the time, but there is a fine line between avoidance of overthinking and mindless degradation.

--
Mundanity is a series of random thoughts of Trilo, reflecting on what is happening in physical or immaterial realms.
